bbPress.org
     __________________________________________________________________

Forums, made the WordPress way

   bbPress is forum software with a twist from the creators of WordPress.
   Easily setup discussion forums inside your WordPress.org powered site.
   Download bbPress ‚Üí
     __________________________________________________________________

Simple Setup

   Simple Setup Easy to setup.
   Easy to moderate.
   Fast, and clean.

Fully Integrated

   Fully Integrated One central account.
   One unified admin area.
   One click install.

Single Installation

   Single Installation Simple step-by-step installation walks you through
   your options.

Multisite Forums

   Multisite Forums Divide your site into sections. Allow your users to
   create content.
